title: The Untold History of Japanese Game Developers DVD + EBOOK
description: Between September and November 2013 John Szczepaniak traveled around Japan interviewing video game developers for a book on the subject of Japanese game development history for a book and dvd. This was originally a Kickstarter project that was funded on June 30, 2013. This is the accompanying DVD, with segments of interview footage, game footage, and other visually interesting material
